   "source": [
    "# 🛡️ SOC-Env: Stable RL Training Loop\n",
    "\n",
    "**Version 2.0 (Zero-Black-Box)**\n",
    "- ✅ **100% Stable**: No `unsloth` or `trl` trainer version conflicts.\n",
    "- ✅ **OpenEnv Compliant**: Native environment wrapping.\n",
    "- ✅ **Real-time Monitoring**: Metrics & reward curves.\n",
    "\n",
    "---"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 🚀 **SINGLE CELL: Setup & Train**\n",
    "1. Paste your `HF_TOKEN` below.\n",
    "2. Ensure Runtime is **T4 GPU**.\n",
    "3. Run the cell."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 1. Setup Environment\n",
    "import os\n",
    "os.environ['HF_TOKEN'] = 'YOUR_TOKEN_HERE'  # <--- PASTE TOKEN HERE\n",
    "os.environ['MODEL_NAME'] = 'Qwen/Qwen2.5-1.5B-Instruct'\n",
    "\n",
    "# 2. Clone Repository (if not already present)\n",
    "REPO_URL = 'https://github.com/taruncodes07/soc-env.git'\n",
    "if not os.path.exists('soc-env'):\n",
    "    !git clone {REPO_URL}\n",
    "    %cd soc-env\n",
    "else:\n",
    "    %cd soc-env\n",
    "    !git pull\n",
    "\n",
    "# 3. Install Stable Stack\n",
    "!pip install -q -r requirements.txt\n",
    "\n",
    "# 4. Run Stable Trainer\n",
    "!python train_rl.py"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
